exam.examName: Staff Selection Commission Junior Engineers - Electrical Engineers
exam.description: SSC JE is an exam conducted by Staff Selection Commission (SSC). This exam is meant for the recruitment of Junior Engineers (JEs) in various branches of Engineering including Civil, Electrical, Mechanical and Quantity Surveying & Contracts.
